# 🏦 Banking Operations Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview

This Power BI dashboard provides a comprehensive view of banking operations by monitoring customer activity, deposits, loans, profitability, and operational performance. It enables stakeholders to track KPIs, compare historical performance, and identify business trends through interactive visualizations.

---

## 🎯 Business Objectives

* Monitor overall banking performance
* Track deposits and loan portfolio
* Analyze revenue, expenses, and net profit
* Compare Current Year (CY) vs Previous Year (PY)
* Identify top-performing branches and regions
* Support data-driven business decisions

---

## 📊 Dashboard Pages

### 1. Executive Overview

* KPI Cards
* Revenue & Profit Trends
* Monthly Performance
* Branch Performance
* Regional Analysis

### 2. Customer Analytics

* Total Customers
* Customer Growth
* Customer Distribution
* Average Account Balance

### 3. Loan & Deposit Analysis

* Total Loans
* Total Deposits
* Loan-to-Deposit Ratio
* Growth Analysis
* Previous Year Comparison

### 4. Financial Performance

* Revenue Analysis
* Expense Analysis
* Net Profit
* Profit Margin
* Financial Trends

